# @accessibility-audit

**WCAG 2.2 AA compliance checker with mobile focus, auto-remediation, and milestone tracking**

## 🎯 Purpose

Ensure your application is accessible to all users, including those with disabilities. **15-20% of users have disabilities**, and **inaccessible websites face legal liability** (ADA lawsuits increased 300% since 2020).

**v3.0.0** adds full WCAG 2.2 compliance checking, mobile accessibility focus, enhanced auto-remediation with rollback capability, and score tracking with milestones for progressive improvement.

**For agencies:** Protects clients from lawsuits, expands user reach, demonstrates quality commitment.

---

