## 📈 Trend Tracking (v3.0.0)

### Accessibility Metrics History

```typescript
interface A11yMetrics {
  timestamp: string;
  overallScore: number;
  levelA: number;
  levelAA: number;
  levelAAA: number;
  criticalIssues: number;
  seriousIssues: number;
